Agency recognizes that there are unmanned, remote campgrounds in the 
national parks system, and requests comment on the means of compliance for 
those systems. 

(3) Rationale 

The sanctioning of Alternative Water as a means of compliance is 
an innovative approach that EPA has developed in recognition of the special 
circumstances and concerns surrounding the sulfate regulation. The proposed 
