This water contains high levels of sulfates. This mineral can cause diarrhea in persons not accustomed to drinking
water with high sulfate content. Persistent diarrhea can cause dehydration. 
Special care should be taken for infants. Bottled water is 
available nearby at

XXXXXXXXXX

.

 


